<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Weather App</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    />
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/favicon1.ico" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css" />
    <script
      src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/e7a61b10ca.js"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-default">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="navbar-header">
          <p class="navbar-brand">AVIV'S TRAINING</p>
          <a class="fas fa-cog settings tt" href="/settings" data-placement="bottom" title="`"></a>
        </div>
          <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
            <li><a class="tt" href="/" data-placement="bottom" title="Z">Can I run?!</a></li>
            <li><a class="tt" href="/gameWorkOut" data-placement="bottom" title="X">Home Workout</a></li>
            <li><a class="tt" href="/sessions" data-placement="bottom" title="C">Statistics</a></li>
          <div class="box2 workOut"></div>
          <input id="hours" value="<%= hours %>" type="hidden" />
          <input id="minutes" value="<%= minutes %>" type="hidden" />
          <input id="seconds" value="<%= seconds %>" type="hidden" />
          <input id="onOff" value="<%= onOff %>" type="hidden" />
        </ul>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <body>
      <div id="whole" class="container">
        <div style="font-size: 2rem;" class="invisble-help">
          <p>Take whatever game you want, make up a rule for doing a set<br>Whenever you break that rule(like dying in the game) you do a set!</p>
          <p>You can change the workout details and functionality in the <a href="/settings" class="tt" data-placement="bottom" title="`">settings</a>!</p>
          <h3>Usage:</h3>
          <p class="rule-list" style="font-size: 2rem;"><b>Add Up:</b> After selecting how many sets, pressing this will calculate the exercise you need to do!</p>
          <p class="rule-list" style="font-size: 2rem;"><b>Go Back:</b> Will take you one repetition back at a time all the way back to 0!</p>
          <p class="rule-list" style="font-size: 2rem;"><b>Reset:</b> Will cancel the workout like you never pressed the "Start Session" button!</p>
          <p class="rule-list" style="font-size: 2rem;"><b>Start Session:</b> Will start the workout(timer will show up), press again to finish the session! <br>
          You can also start a session by pressing the "Add Up" button for the first time!</p>
          <h3>Rules ideas:</h3>
          <p class="rule-list">>Whenever you die you do a set.</p>
          <p class="rule-list">>At the end of a match you calculate the kill death ratio and do a number of sets.</p>
          <p class="rule-list">>Hard: Whenever someone does a specific thing do a set(example:whenever someone jump).</p>
          <p class="rule-list">>Do a set every X minutes(BORING)</p>
        </div>
        <h1>Game Workout!<i class="fas fa-info-circle info-icn"></i></h1>
        <p>
          Simple web application that monitors your workouts! <br />
          This one specifically monitors game workouts.
        </p>
        <form action="/gameWorkOut" method="POST">
          <input type="radio" class="tt" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="0-9" id="mult1" name="mult" value="1" checked />
          <label class="tt" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="0-9" for="mult1">1</label>
          <input type="radio" class="tt" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="0-9" id="mult2" name="mult" value="2" />
          <label class="tt" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="0-9" for="mult2">2</label>
          <input type="radio" class="tt" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="0-9" id="mult3" name="mult" value="3" />
          <label class="tt" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="0-9" for="mult3">3</label><br />
          <input type="radio" class="tt" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="0-9" id="mult4" name="mult" value="4" />
          <label class="tt" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="0-9" for="mult4">4</label>
          <input type="radio" class="tt" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="0-9" id="mult5" name="mult" value="5" />
          <label class="tt" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="0-9" for="mult5">5</label>
          <input type="radio" class="tt" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="0-9" id="mult6" name="mult" value="6" />
          <label class="tt" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="0-9" for="mult6">6</label><br />
          <input type="radio" class="tt" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="0-9" id="mult7" name="mult" value="7" />
          <label class="tt" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="0-9" for="mult7">7</label>
          <input type="radio" class="tt" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="0-9" id="mult8" name="mult" value="8" />
          <label class="tt" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="0-9" for="mult8">8</label>
          <input type="radio" class="tt" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="0-9" id="mult9" name="mult" value="9" />
          <label class="tt" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="0-9" for="mult9">9</label>
          <input type="radio" class="tt" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="0-9" id="mult0" name="mult" value="0"/>
          <label class="tt" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="0-9" for="mult0">0</label><br /><br />
          <button data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Spacebar"
            id="add"
            name="action"
            value="add"
            class="btn my-btn tt"
            type="submit"
          >
            Add Up
          </button>
          <button data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="Backspace"
            id="back"
            name="action"
            value="back"
            class="btn my-btn tt"
            type="submit"
          >
            Go Back
          </button>
          <button data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="R"
            id="reset"
            name="action"
            value="reset"
            class="btn my-btn tt"
            type="submit"
          >
            Reset
          </button>
        </form>

        <form action="/addSession" method="POST">
          <div class="container-fluid total-work">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-12">
                <div id="plus1" class="added invis">+<%= firstExer %></div>
                <h3><%= setting.exercises[0].exerciseName %>: </h3>
                <p id="sum1" class="totalSet"><%= totalFirstExer %></p>
                <input id="totalEx1"
                  type="hidden"
                  name="firstExercise"
                  value="<%= totalFirstExer %>"
                />
                <input type="hidden" name="exerciseName1" value="<%= setting.exercises[0].exerciseName %>">
                <input type="hidden" id="goal1" value="<%= setting.exercises[0].goal %>">
                <input type="hidden" id="type1" value="<%= setting.exercises[0].type %>">
              </div>
              <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-12">
                <div id="plus2" class="added invis">+<%= secondExer %></div>
                <h3><%= setting.exercises[1].exerciseName %>:</h3>
                <p id="sum2" class="totalSet"><%= totalSecondExer %></p>
                <input id="totalEx2"
                  type="hidden"
                  name="secondExercise"
                  value="<%= totalSecondExer %>"
                />
                <input type="hidden" name="exerciseName2" value="<%= setting.exercises[1].exerciseName %>">
                <input type="hidden" id="goal2" value="<%= setting.exercises[1].goal %>">
                <input type="hidden" id="type2" value="<%= setting.exercises[1].type %>">
              </div>
              <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-12">
                <div id="plus3" class="added invis">+<%= thirdExer %></div>
                <h3><%= setting.exercises[2].exerciseName %>:</h3>
                <p id="sum3" class="totalSet"><%= totalThirdExer %></p>
                <input id="totalEx3"
                  type="hidden"
                  name="thirdExercise"
                  value="<%= totalThirdExer %>"
                />
                <input type="hidden" name="exerciseName3" value="<%= setting.exercises[2].exerciseName %>">
                <input type="hidden" id="goal3" value="<%= setting.exercises[2].goal %>">
                <input type="hidden" id="type3" value="<%= setting.exercises[2].type %>">
              </div>
              <input
                type="hidden"
                id="pressedStart"
                value="<%= pressedStart %>"
              />
              <input
                type="hidden"
                id="pressedDelete"
                value="<%= pressedDelete %>"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
          <button data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="F"
            id="session"
            class="btn my-btn btn-lg btn-block tt"
            type="submit"
          ><%= sessionButton %></button>
        </form>
        <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-Tc5IQib027qvyjSMfHjOMaLkfuWVxZxUPnCJA7l2mCWNIpG9mGCD8wGNIcPD7Txa" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <script src="/js/global.js"></script>
        <script src="/js/gameWorkOut.js"></script>

        <%- include("partials/footer") %>
      </div>
    </body>
  </head>
</html>
